Banco Comercial Portugues Analyzes Options for Poland’s Bank Millennium

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-07-27T16:31:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/banco-comercial-portugues-analyzes-options-for-poland-s-bank-millennium.html
Banco Comercial Portugues SA (BCP) ,
 Portugal ’s second-biggest lender by market value, said it’s
analyzing the options of its business in Poland with the help of
external advisors.  The Portuguese bank said it’s also “exploring options” to
reduce its exposure to the Greek market, according to a
regulatory filing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
